Name: Hl7EuDocumentTypes
Title: HL7 EU Document Types
Description: Document types (templates) as defined by HL7 EU. It identifies the type and template of the document.

Name: DiagnosticReportSupportingInfoCodeSystem
Title: Diagnostic Report Support Info Code System
Description: Code system for codes to be used in `DiagnosticReport.supportInfo` for imaging reports.

Name: Hl7EuImagingEndpointTerminologyCodeSystem
Title: CodeSystem for terminology used in Endpoint resources in the EU Imaging IG.
Description: This code system defines various codes used to define ValueSets for Endpoints within the HL7-EU imaging IG.

Name: MissingDicomTerminology
Title: Missing DICOM Terminology
Description: Code system for codes that are defined in DICOM but for which no matching code system is available in FHIR.
